building_description:
Canal Cove Villas is a luxury project developed by Nakheel Properties, located on the renowned Palm Jumeirah in Dubai. Completed in 2007, this complex comprises a mix of villas and townhouses, boasting a Mediterranean-inspired architectural style.
Property Details
In total, there are 118 buildings within Canal Cove Villas, divided into six zones, each containing 6 to 12 buildings. Each zone features its own courtyard with a swimming pool, providing residents with exclusive leisure facilities. The properties within Canal Cove Villas offer a choice of 3 and 4-bedroom homes, starting from 3,800 sq ft in size. The starting price for these properties begins at AED 8,000,000 (USD 2,178,000) as of 2020.
Location and Accessibility
Canal Cove Villas offer a private oceanfront location on Palm Jumeirah, providing residents with a serene environment away from the bustling city. However, it remains conveniently close to the main infrastructure of Dubai. The development is easily accessible, with Dubai International Airport reachable within 30 minutes by car. The Business Bay business district and the iconic Burj Khalifa skyscraper in the Downtown area are both approximately a 20-minute drive away.
The Palm Jumeirah island itself offers a plethora of attractions and facilities for residents. Nearby attractions include the Aquaventure Waterpark, The Pointe, and Nakheel Mall, providing entertainment, dining, and shopping options. Additionally, the area is home to several nurseries, clinics, and schools, ensuring convenience for families residing in Canal Cove Villas.
Canal Cove Villas on Palm Jumeirah offer luxury waterfront living with Mediterranean charm. With its exclusive amenities, convenient location, and proximity to key attractions and facilities, it presents an ideal residential option for discerning individuals and families seeking upscale living in Dubai.

Palmera at Arabian Ranches is a serene, Mediterranean-inspired villa community nestled within the larger Arabian Ranches development in Dubai. Known for its distinct architecture and tranquil ambiance, Palmera offers a range of two- and three-bedroom villas designed with charming terracotta roofs, arched windows, and lush, landscaped gardens.
The community is divided into four sub-clusters, each featuring its own park and swimming pool, providing residents with a peaceful and family-friendly environment. Palmera’s villas are set amidst winding pathways, palm-lined streets, and tranquil courtyards, creating a picturesque setting that promotes a sense of community and relaxation.
Residents enjoy access to an array of world-class amenities, including the Arabian Ranches Golf Club, equestrian center, tennis courts, and a well-equipped fitness center. The development also includes shopping and dining options at the nearby Arabian Ranches Retail Centre, schools, and healthcare facilities, making it an ideal location for families.
With its strategic location near key road networks, Palmera provides easy access to Dubai’s major attractions and business districts, making it a highly desirable community for those seeking a blend of comfort, luxury, and convenience in a prime residential setting.

Welcome to Villanova, a neighbourhood that you can call your own. Mediterranean inspired cluster homes, townhouses, villas and apartments along with vast open spaces create a serene atmosphere where the community becomes an extended family, and the neighbours become friends.

Arabian Ranches’ newest community, Reem, is the next chapter in Ranches living. Infused with lush landscaping, Reem is home to bright and spacious townhouses within the master-planned community. The architecture of the townhomes exemplifies Simplicity, Elegance and Serenity. Great care was taken on creating a beautiful façade through harmony, balance, touch and texture. An architectural style that respects and connects the rich heritage of Dubai’s past to the future in a contemporary way.
Choose from three and four bedroom townhouses that offer generous accommodation, with multi-functional spaces to suit your individual lifestyle and family needs.
The Springs is an established gated community that has redefined modern living in Dubai. The Springs comprises clusters of townhouses set as distinct precincts, each with dedicated entry points.

Casa Viva is a new phase of Serena located in Dubailand by Dubai Properties. Just like previous phases in Serena, Casa Viva will be a collection of elegantly designed townhouses surrounded by lush greenery in a peaceful community. 
Development Highlights:

Relax and unwind in spacious Portuguese-styled 2 & 3 bedroom townhouses.
Recreation Community Centre with gym and swimming pool facilities for an active lifestyle.
Located within Dubailand with direct access to Emirates Road for convenient travel.
Enjoy a host of amenities at the Central Plaza in the heart of the community.
Suitable payment plans to move into your dream home.

Expo Valley is an exclusive residential community located within Expo City Dubai, offering a harmonious blend of natural beauty and urban convenience. The development is designed with a focus on sustainability and well-being, featuring spacious villas and townhouses surrounded by lush greenery, lakes, and a wadi. The community promotes eco-friendly living with smart homes and environmentally conscious infrastructure, including pedestrian pathways, cycling trails, and dedicated routes for e-scooters.
Residents of Expo Valley enjoy privacy while remaining well-connected to the vibrant surroundings. The community features a range of premium amenities, including clubhouses, gyms, wellness centers, outdoor cinemas, and family-friendly spaces such as playgrounds and parks. A unique 'green link' corridor provides access to Expo City Dubai attractions, creating a seamless connection to the city’s commercial, entertainment, and cultural hubs.
Expo Valley’s thoughtful design also incorporates the area’s natural topography, creating a microclimate that reduces noise and dust, enhancing the overall quality of life. The community offers an ideal living environment for those seeking luxury, sustainability, and convenience in one of Dubai’s most innovative residential destinations.

Rivana at The Valley presents an exquisite collection of 3, 4, and 5-bedroom twin villas, where modern living harmoniously blends with the beauty of nature. This stunning residential development offers residents an unparalleled lifestyle in the heart of Dubai, with starting prices from 2.8 million AED.
Nestled within The Valley, a quaint new town conceived to inspire a sense of tranquility and harmony, Rivana showcases contemporary townhouse complexes surrounded by the mesmerizing panorama of shimmering sands and lush green open spaces. As you step into this picturesque community, life takes on new meaning, where serenity meets convenience and inspiration greets everyday living.
Perfectly positioned on the Dubai-Al Ain Road, Rivana enjoys easy access to all major areas of Dubai and the neighboring emirate of Abu Dhabi. Whether you seek the vibrant city life or the serene embrace of nature, Rivana brings you closer to both, ensuring every aspect of your lifestyle is effortlessly catered to.
Rivana's twin villas are thoughtfully designed to offer spacious and well-appointed interiors, creating a harmonious living space for families of all sizes. Each villa is crafted with attention to detail and modern finishes, providing residents with a haven of comfort and elegance.
Indulge in a life of convenience and luxury within this oasis, where an array of premium amenities awaits you. Whether you seek relaxation or recreation, Rivana has something for everyone. Enjoy leisurely strolls amidst the verdant landscapes, unwind at the inviting community pool, or keep yourself fit and active at the state-of-the-art fitness center. Rivana promises to fulfill all your desires and aspirations.
Embrace a lifestyle of unparalleled convenience and connectivity, with The Valley's strategic location offering quick and easy access to key destinations across Dubai and Abu Dhabi. Commute with ease to business districts, educational institutions, and retail hubs, making every day a seamless journey of productivity and enjoyment.
Discover Rivana at The Valley, where modern elegance meets natural beauty, and the dream of an idyllic home becomes a delightful reality. Experience the essence of contemporary living in this extraordinary oasis, and embark on a journey of boundless opportunities, serenity, and inspiration.

Jasmine Lane by Elie Saab is an exclusive residential development situated in the prestigious Jumeirah Golf Estates in Dubai. This luxurious project is brought to life through the partnership of Durar Group and Fortune 5. The development is expected to reach completion by the third quarter of 2024.
Residence Features
Jasmine Lane offers a total of 138 elegantly designed 3-bedroom townhouses. These spacious residences range from 2,201 to 2,332 square feet and are entirely designed by renowned fashion house, Elie Saab. Each townhouse combines luxury and practicality, featuring engineered oak and herringbone parquet flooring in the bedrooms, while porcelain calacatta with a gold effect adorns the main areas.
In-House Amenities
Every townhouse in Jasmine Lane comes with a private swimming pool, a two-car garage, a maid’s room with an en-suite bathroom, along with a large living/dining area. The master bedrooms offer ample space with walk-in closets. Additional bedrooms are fitted with built-in wardrobes, and the kitchens are equipped with high-end appliances such as a fridge, cooker, and microwave from Siemens or a comparable brand.
Community Amenities
Jasmine Lane residents will have access to a variety of luxurious community amenities. These include a clubhouse with adult and junior swimming pools, an indoor gymnasium, sauna and steam rooms, a sports zone, an outdoor fitness area, and a secret lagoon. Outdoor entertainment areas and beautifully landscaped gardens provide perfect spots for relaxation. For the convenience of visitors, 26 guest parking spaces will be available.

Nima at The Valley is an exquisite residential project nestled within the captivating town of The Valley in Dubai. This project offers a harmonious blend of modern living, ecological elegance, and an abundance of amenities, making it an ideal choice for those seeking a luxurious and nature-inspired lifestyle.
The Valley: A Self-Sufficient Community
Situated amidst the stunning juxtaposition of shimmering sands and lush green open spaces, The Valley itself is a self-sufficient community designed to cater to the diverse needs and preferences of its residents. It boasts a comprehensive array of lifestyle amenities, educational institutions, healthcare services, leisure activities, and recreational facilities, all set within a picturesque and serene backdrop.
Nima: The Epitome of Luxury and Nature
Ecological Elegance
Nima sets itself apart by seamlessly blending modern living with the gentle caress of nature. Its architecture and design are a testament to ecological elegance, creating a living environment that is both sophisticated and environmentally conscious.
Neighborhood Serenity
Nima is located in one of Dubai's most elegant neighborhoods, ensuring residents experience tranquility and a sense of exclusivity within this vibrant city.
Waterway Wonders
A unique feature of Nima is its intricate waterway network, which not only provides residents with stunning water views but also connects hearts through serene vistas at every turn. Living at Nima is an invitation to immerse oneself in the symphony of nature's best.
Tailored Homes
Each townhouse in Nima, whether a 3 or 4-bedroom unit, is a crafted masterpiece designed to resonate with discerning tastes. These homes reflect unconfined creativity and meticulous attention to detail.
Premium Amenities
Nima offers a wealth of premium amenities, including an exclusive clubhouse, regal gatehouses, wellness zones, and more. Luxury is redefined at every corner, ensuring that residents enjoy a life of opulence.
A Plethora of Facilities
From the shimmering Golden Beach to the vibrant Town Centre and serene barbecue spots, Nima provides a plethora of facilities that cater to various recreational and leisure preferences. Residents are always surrounded by luxury.
Environmentally Conscious Living
Nima's commitment to environmental sustainability is evident in its use of locally sourced materials, celebrating the surrounding landscape while minimizing its ecological footprint.
Celebration of Nature
With unique waterways and proximity to the majestic Valley Park, every day at Nima is a celebration of nature's opulence. Residents have the privilege of waking up to serene views and embracing a lifestyle connected to the natural world.
Location and Accessibility
Nima enjoys a strategic location on the Dubai-Al Ain Road, providing easy access to all major areas of Dubai. Residents can also relish beautiful views of verdant green landscapes. Moreover, Nima is conveniently located just 5 minutes from the Rugby Sevens Stadium, 8 minutes from the Dubai Outlet Mall, 25 minutes from the iconic Burj Khalifa & Downtown Dubai, and a mere 25 minutes from Dubai International Airport.
Payment Plan and Completion Date
The payment plan for Nima is structured as 90-10, allowing for flexibility in securing these luxurious townhouses. The completion date for this project is anticipated to be in July 2027, offering a clear timeline for future residents.
Starting Price and Unit Availability
Nima at The Valley presents a range of 3 and 4-bedroom townhouses, with a starting price of 2.1 million AED. There are a total of 520 meticulously designed units available, ensuring a diverse range of options to suit various preferences and family sizes.

Sandoval Lane provides a unique living experience in the heart of Jumeirah Village Circle (JVC). Known for its family-friendly environment, this community features a mix of stylish townhouses that blend comfort with modern architecture. Residents benefit from easy access to major highways and public transportation, ensuring seamless connectivity throughout Dubai. The area is enriched with parks, schools, shopping centers, and leisure facilities, creating a well-rounded lifestyle.
Key Features:


Prime Location: Sandoval Lane is strategically located with easy access to Sheikh Mohammed Bin Zayed Road and Al Khail Road, facilitating effortless commuting to other parts of Dubai.


Modern Living Spaces: The townhouses are designed with contemporary aesthetics, featuring spacious interiors and well-planned layouts that cater to modern family needs.


Community Amenities: Residents can enjoy an array of amenities, including parks, sports facilities, and nearby retail options, enhancing the overall living experience.


Educational Options: The community is surrounded by several reputable schools, offering a range of curricula, which makes it an attractive choice for families.


Recreational Activities: JVC boasts numerous parks and green spaces, along with access to nearby golf courses and sports complexes, promoting an active lifestyle.


Sandoval Lane is perfect for those seeking a balanced lifestyle in a community that offers both modern living and accessibility to essential services and recreational activities. With its strategic location and family-oriented facilities, it stands out as a desirable choice in Dubai.

7 West Villas is a contemporary townhouse development located in the vibrant Jumeirah Village Circle (JVC). Developed by A.S.A 1 Developers Limited, this community features a row of 14 freehold properties designed for comfortable family living. The project was completed in 2016, offering a blend of style and functionality, making it a perfect choice for both investors and end-users.
Key Features:

Property Type: Townhouses
Unit Configuration: Each townhouse includes:

Ground Floor: Maid's room, two garages, a garden, and a guest powder room.
First Floor: Two bedrooms, a lobby, and a balcony.
Second Floor: One additional bedroom with a large terrace and balcony.


Amenities: The development boasts modern amenities including:

A fully equipped kitchen
Central air-conditioning
24/7 security and video surveillance
Covered parking
Access to community parks and children's play areas
Proximity to retail outlets and supermarkets


Community Feel: 7 West Villas is set within a lush, landscaped environment, offering a peaceful residential experience with easy access to key roadways.

Conclusion: 7 West Villas combines modern living with a community-oriented environment in Jumeirah Village Circle. With its well-thought-out design and convenient amenities, it stands out as a desirable residential choice in Dubai.
Westar Les Maisonettes developed by Westar Properties features a row of 15 G+2 four bedroom townhouses in District 10 of Jumeirah Village Circle.

Located in the heart of Dubai, The Lakes is a prestigious residential neighborhood. It is a peaceful and scenic area designed by the master developers, Emaar Properties, with rivers, lush greenery and landscaped parks. Ghadeer is one of The Lakes' six developed communities and, as the name implies, the community offers its residents a serene atmosphere.

Casa Flores is a well-established residential community in Motor City, renowned for its spacious villas that provide a perfect blend of comfort and style. This charming neighborhood is ideal for families and individuals looking for a serene lifestyle, enhanced by the array of facilities and attractions nearby.
Key Features:


Spacious Living: The villas in Casa Flores are designed with open floor plans, offering ample living space, modern finishes, and private gardens, catering to those who appreciate spacious living environments.


Prime Location: Situated in Motor City, residents enjoy quick access to major roadways such as Sheikh Mohammed Bin Zayed Road and Al Khail Road, making commutes to key areas in Dubai convenient.


Amenities and Facilities: The community is well-equipped with essential amenities, including supermarkets, schools, and healthcare facilities. Nearby options include Blue Mart Supermarket, GEMS Metropole School, and HealthBay Motor City clinic.


Recreational Options: Casa Flores is surrounded by numerous parks and leisure activities, including proximity to Dubai Autodrome and Dubai Miracle Garden, making it ideal for families looking for outdoor fun.


Shopping and Dining: Residents have access to several malls and dining options, including First Avenue Mall and various restaurants offering diverse cuisines, enhancing the overall lifestyle experience in the community.


Casa Flores represents an attractive living option for those seeking a peaceful yet connected lifestyle in one of Dubai's vibrant neighborhoods. With its spacious villas, convenient amenities, and recreational offerings, it provides a well-rounded community atmosphere for families and individuals alike.

Welcome to Alana, a premium residential community located in The Valley, Dubai. This project offers an idyllic blend of nature, luxury, and resort-style amenities, making it the perfect retreat from the urban hustle and bustle. Alana is the brainchild of Emaar Properties, renowned for iconic developments such as Boulevard Heights, Sunrise Bay, South Beach, and The Oasis, and it is slated for completion in May 2027.
Lush Greenery and Scenic Views
Alana offers an abundance of greenery, walkways, relaxation areas, children's playgrounds, and sports grounds. It provides residents with a serene environment surrounded by nature, making it an ideal sanctuary for single professionals, couples, and businessmen.
Luxury Living
Alana features white-colored 3–5 bedroom twin villas with living areas ranging from 3,720 sq. ft to 4,977 sq. ft. These residences offer a private garden and are in close proximity to the waterfront. Choose from two architectural facades: Sierra and Lilac, each reflecting urban elegance and contemporary design.
Tranquil Interiors
The interiors of Alana villas boast a serene color scheme, with tones of pistachio, grey, beige, brown, and white. The contemporary design, stylish finishes, and urban sophistication create an inviting living space. Each twin villa includes a semi-closed fully-fitted kitchen, a maid's room, separate formal and informal living rooms, and bedrooms with access to balconies. The rooftop terrace offers a family lounge with breathtaking sunset views.
Resort-Like Amenities
Residents of Alana will have access to a host of luxury amenities, including an outdoor fitness area, a pocket park, a recreation lawn, a community center, and a central open pond with river cascades. These amenities complement the peaceful living environment.
Proximity to Key Venues
Alana is strategically located near key entertainment and leisure venues in The Valley. The Pavilion features an observation tower, Zen and Oasis gardens, and areas for yoga classes. Golden Beach offers a resort-like experience with water splash activities, children's play areas, and cafes. The Sports Village includes sports courts, an outdoor gymnasium, and cycling and jogging tracks. Families with children will appreciate Kids' Dale, which features rock climbing activities, an amphitheater, and an archeological play area.
Accessibility
The Valley is conveniently located, with easy access to major highways, key financial areas, and educational institutions. Downtown Dubai and Business Bay are a 25-minute drive away, and both Dubai International Airport and Al Maktoum International Airport are within half an hour.
Shopping and Entertainment
Shopping enthusiasts will find Dubai Outlet Mall just a 10-minute drive away, featuring over 240 retail stores, including renowned brands. Other shopping options include Silicon Central Mall, Villanova Community Mall, Cedre Shopping Centre, and Q1 Mall.
Sports and Leisure
Sports enthusiasts can enjoy The Sevens Stadium and Al Habtoor Polo Resort, located nearby. Additionally, attractions like Global Village and IMG Worlds of Adventure are just a 20-minute drive away.
Investment Potential
A residence in Alana offers not only a luxurious living experience but also a compelling investment opportunity. With an average ROI of 6.4% for 3-bedroom villas in the surrounding areas, Alana villas are likely to be in high demand, especially among families with children and those who value comfort and privacy.
Golden Visa Opportunity
Purchasing a twin villa in Alana opens the door to a 10-year Golden visa application, which can also be extended to family members and household staff. This visa can be maintained as long as you remain the owner of the property, making it an attractive investment benefit.
Alana presents a unique opportunity to experience luxury, nature, and tranquility in a prime Dubai location while providing a promising investment path for the future.

In a captivating debut, Aldar presents the Haven in the heart of Dubailand. This project signifies a pioneering venture into Dubai's residential landscape, offering a unique living experience that prioritizes community-wide wellness. 
Nestled beneath the comforting canopy of a treehouse and accompanied by the gentle serenade of a flowing stream, Haven is a testament to the commitment of Aldar to create a thriving, interconnected, and well-being-centered community.
Key Details
Location
Haven finds its place in the vibrant community of Dubailand, strategically positioned to offer residents a blend of tranquility and accessibility.
Unit Variety
The development boasts a diverse array of living options, featuring 2,428 residential units, which include villas, townhouses, and apartments. The unit configurations are as follows:


Elite Haven Villas: These spacious 4-6 bedroom villas offer an exclusive and luxurious living experience.


Serene Villas: Thoughtfully designed 3-5 bedroom homes are perfect for families seeking a balanced lifestyle.


Park Haven Townhouses: The 3-4 bedroom townhouses cater to those who appreciate the convenience of townhouse living.


Pricing and Payment Plans
Unit prices start at AED 2.5 million. A range of flexible payment plans ensures that prospective residents can choose the option that aligns with their financial preferences.


Serene Villas and Park Haven Townhouses: These units follow a 60/40 payment plan, allowing a balanced approach to investment.


Elite Haven Villas: With a 70/30 payment structure, this option offers more flexibility in payments.


A minimal 5% down payment is required, making it accessible to a wide range of potential homeowners.


Handover Date
The anticipated handover date for Haven is set for the third quarter of 2027 (Q3, 2027).
Luxury Amenities
Haven stands out as a community that places wellness and convenience at the forefront of its design. The development offers an extensive range of amenities to cater to the diverse needs and lifestyles of its residents:
Wellness and Recreation
The Wellness Centre and Air Fitness facilities provide dedicated spaces for residents to focus on their physical and mental well-being. Haven Central Park and The Green offer lush green spaces for relaxation and community gatherings. For those seeking spiritual solace, a Mosque is available within the community.
Leisure Facilities
The Plunge Pool, Basketball Court, and Run & Ride Tracks cater to the active lifestyle needs of the residents. A Smart Community approach leverages technology to enhance community living.
Relaxation and Entertainment
Reflexology Paths and Retail Therapy options offer relaxation and shopping convenience within the community. Families with young children will appreciate the presence of Little Haven, a Nursery and Kindergarten, as well as the Splash Pool for kids. Adults can unwind at the Tranquility Pool, while Padel Haven offers social and recreational opportunities for Padel enthusiasts.
Why Choose Haven
Haven is a remarkable testament to Aldar's commitment to fostering a holistic living experience in Dubai. Beyond being just a place to reside, Haven is a haven for well-being, community, and quality living.
Every moment at Haven is thoughtfully curated to enhance the residents' quality of life, making it a harmonious and vibrant community where individuals and families can thrive. Experience the tranquility, well-being, and harmony of Haven - a remarkable addition to Dubai's residential landscape.

Nad Al Sheba Gardens Phase 4 by Meraas presents an exceptional living experience through its luxury collection of 3-bedroom townhouses and 4, 5 & 6-bedroom villas, situated in the heart of Nad Al Sheba, Dubai. This development goes beyond the ordinary, crafting a sanctuary for ambition and purpose, distinct from any other community in Dubai. It caters to contemporary passions, offering a seamless blend of comfort, nature, and community.
Location Excellence:
Positioned just ten minutes away from Downtown Dubai, this development enjoys a covetable location with easy access to the Meydan Racetrack and various premium leisure and lifestyle amenities. Residents benefit from proximity to Dubai International Airport and major highways, making exploration of Dubai and beyond effortlessly convenient. Here, residents can relish the tranquility of nature and the convenience of the city, all within reach.
Immersive Living Experience:
The villas and townhouses are strategically positioned to provide an unparalleled living experience. Surrounded by scenic landscapes, these distinguished homes achieve a modern and refined look, with sunlight generously suffusing the living areas, creating a seamless connection with nature. It's not just a home; it's an immersive experience, waking up to the splendor of nature every day.
Extraordinary Amenities:
The development excels in offering extraordinary experiences with a yoga lawn for rejuvenation, running tracks amidst lush flora, and meticulously designed sports and leisure facilities. A sparkling swimming pool, a state-of-the-art gymnasium, and a wave pool, an aquatic playground, contribute to a vibrant and active lifestyle. The events lawn and amphitheatre provide a lively open-air canvas for arts and entertainment.
Key Highlights:


Diverse selection of 3-bedroom townhouses and 4, 5, and 6-bedroom villas catering to various family sizes and lifestyles.


A new residential development in Nad Al Sheba, Dubai, offering a unique and luxurious living experience.


Conveniently located minutes away from Downtown Dubai, with easy access to Meydan Racetrack and premium leisure amenities.


Architectural design inspired by comfort, nature, and community, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.


Private gated community ensuring the highest level of security and exclusivity.


Wide array of facilities including walkable roads, cycling paths, and running tracks for an active and outdoor lifestyle.


Nad Al Sheba Gardens Phase 4 offers residents the opportunity to seamlessly integrate all aspects of their lives, creating a home that perfectly aligns with present and future lifestyle aspirations.

Taormina Village at Wadi Al Safa: A Luxurious Residential Haven in Dubailand
Taormina Village at Wadi Al Safa stands as the latest residential epitome developed by Reportage Properties, offering an exquisite selection of 3 & 4-bedroom townhouses and 4 & 5-bedroom villas in the dynamic Dubailand. This project, featuring 530 meticulously designed residences, sets a new benchmark in high-end living, emphasizing contemporary design, quality craftsmanship, and environmental sustainability.
Strategic Location for Distinctive Living
Situated strategically in Wadi Al Safa, Dubailand, Taormina Village ensures residents enjoy a distinctive and contemporary lifestyle. Surrounded by parks, schools, mosques, and community retails, the development fulfills all desires. Its proximity to major attractions in Dubai makes it an ideal choice for those seeking a well-rounded and convenient living experience.
Architectural Brilliance and Design Excellence
Taormina Village showcases architectural brilliance and design excellence, with residences crafted to the highest international standards. The emphasis on environmental sustainability in Dubailand enhances the appeal of the development, providing luxury amidst a green, clean environment.
Meticulously Crafted Residences
The residences feature private balconies, terrace with unit-specific plans, kitchens with cabinets and countertops, and double-glazed windows for energy efficiency and sound insulation. Central air conditioning ensures optimal comfort for residents.
Recreational Retreat with Amenities
